We wanted to let you know your card was billed automatically for the amount of <%= "#{number_to_currency(@invoice[:amount].to_d/100)} #{@invoice[:currency].upcase}" %>.
</p>

<h3>Invoice ID</h3>
<%= @invoice[:id] %>
<h3>Plan</h3>
<%= @invoice[:plan_id] %>
