<%= "****-****-****-#{@user.subscription.last_4_digits}" %>

<p>
Just a reminder, you can edit your subscription or billing details at any time here:
<%== edit_subscription_url(@user.subscription) %>
</p>

<p>
Thanks, let us know if you have any questions.
</p>
